concluded a $1.35 billion accord to form Rizk RED House
Healthcare, a venture that will develop 10 specialized hospitals
in  Saudi Arabia  with an overall capacity of 3,000 beds, the
Beirut-based  Daily Star  reported.  Rizk RED House Healthcare will have its headquarters in
